name: Dirty Addiction Swarovski Rhinestoned Brass Knuckles
description:
The famous Dirty Addiction Brass Knuckle necklace.  Show 'em you're tough and sexy with this rhinestone-embellished brass knuckle pendant.  Features a silver mirrored acrylic pendant embellished with genuine ice clear Swarovski crystal rhinestones.  Chunky chain measures approximately 14" in length.

Measures 3 x 2"

Hangs off two 7" chains

***

This necklace is delicate and while suitable for every day wear, should be handled and worn with care.
